reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easiest to install, quality, great feel!
reviews.reviewText: I have gone through screen savers by the dozens, I’ve paid the $50 premium ones from the Apple Store with lifetime guarantee , only to find they don’t honor it ! You have to send back screen to Belkin and they send you one then you pay apple to install. This product is far superior , you get two screen savers and installation . Quality of glass is the best I’ve found! Highly recommend !

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 19, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great screen protector for iPhone X
reviews.reviewText: I drop my phone all the time, it’s really just ridiculous how often. This protected my phone for about a 1.5 years. The only reason the screen protector finally cracked was because my phone case broken and then I dropped my phone on a concrete sidewalk. Anyhoo, it still saved my actual phone screen from cracking. I just put on the second screen protector and it’s very easy to install with the video guide.
